prites, and variable blood/gore settings.\n\nUnusually, there are two European versions of the game: one uses the title Light Bringer, and the other uses the title Dungeon Magic. While this game uses the same title as Taito's earlier NES game Dungeon Magic: Sword of the Elements, the two games are unrelated aside from their titles.","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/lightbringer","videos":[{"id":129945,"video_id":"PxtefKqsodk"}],"websites":[{"id":369872,"url":"https://www.twitch.tv/directory/game/Lightbringer","type":{"id":6,"type":"Twitch"}}]}